<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - Kraya & Kuber</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kode+Mono:wght@400..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            /* Increased font size */
            margin: 20px 20px 0px 20px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px 20px 15px 20px;
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 18px;
            /* Increased font size */
        }

        .otp-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .otp {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #333333;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            /* Increased font size */
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            /* Increased font size */
            color: #999999;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #0070f3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .headerLogoText {
            font-size: 45px;
            color: #05a000;
            font-family: 'Kode Mono', 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif !important;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
        }

        ::selection {
            color: #000000;
            background: #d1d1d1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="headerLogoText">KiiT EPASS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="greeting">
            Hello {{userName}},
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Password Reset!</p>
            <p>To verify your account reset, please use the following OTP:</p>
            <div class="otp-container">
                <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
            </div>
            <p>This OTP is valid for 15 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Requested from IP: {{ip}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to mail us on <a href="mailto:heapmindofficial@gmail.com">heapmindofficial@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>